36–37: TEXT SECTION UNDER MAIN IMAGE
──────────────────────────────────────────────

Text Section Table
- Place under main image
- Syntax:
  <table width="100%" border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0">
    <tr>
      <td height="72" align="center" valign="top">
        <table border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0">
          <tr>
            <td width="26" align="center">
              <font face="Verdana, Geneva, sans-serif" color="#000000">
                Your text goes here
              </font>
            </td>
          </tr>
        </table>
      </td>
    </tr>
  </table>
- Notes:
  * Height = 72px
  * Horizontal alignment = center
  * Vertical alignment = top
  * Nested table controls width & font styling

