38: CONTACT US BUTTON + NEWSLETTER FORM
──────────────────────────────────────────────

Contact Button Table
- Outer table:
  <table width="100%" border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0">
    <tr>
      <td height="72" align="center" valign="top">
        <table width="313" border="0" cellspacing="3" cellpadding="3" bgcolor="#FFA500">
          <tr>
            <td width="301" align="center" nowrap>
              <font face="Verdana, Geneva, sans-serif" color="#FFFFFF" size="5">
                <a href="#">Contact Us Today</a>
              </font>
            </td>
          </tr>
        </table>
      </td>
    </tr>
  </table>
- Notes:
  * Height = 72px
  * Alignment center, vertical top
  * Nested table orange background (#FFA500)
  * Link placeholder: href="#"
  * Font color white, size 5

Newsletter Registration Form
- Outer table row:
  <tr>
    <td height="72" align="center" valign="top">
      <h3>Register for Our Newsletter</h3>
      <form name="contact" method="post" action="send.php">
        <input type="text" name="email">
        <input type="submit" value="Submit">
      </form>
    </td>
  </tr>
- Notes:
  * Form uses POST method
  * Action = send.php
  * Input name = "email"
  * Submit button included

──────────────────────────────────────────────
39: THREE-COLUMN INFO TABLE
──────────────────────────────────────────────

Three-Column Table
- Outer table:
  <table width="100%" border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0">
    <tr>
      <td>
        <table border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0">
          <tr>
            <!-- Column Headings -->
            <td width="268" align="center">
              <font face="Verdana, Geneva, sans-serif"><strong>About Us</strong></font>
            </td>
            <td width="268" align="center">
              <font face="Verdana, Geneva, sans-serif"><strong>Our Vision</strong></font>
            </td>
            <td width="290" align="center">
              <font face="Verdana, Geneva, sans-serif"><strong>Services</strong></font>
            </td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <!-- Column Content -->
            <td width="268" valign="top">
              <font face="Verdana, Geneva, sans-serif">
                Some descriptive text about the company.
              </font>
            </td>
            <td width="268" valign="top">
              <font face="Verdana, Geneva, sans-serif">
                Our mission and vision statement.
              </font>
            </td>
            <td width="290" valign="top">
              <font face="Verdana, Geneva, sans-serif">
                <ul>
                  <li>Service 1</li>
                  <li>Service 2</li>
                  <li>Service 3</li>
                </ul>
              </font>
            </td>
          </tr>
        </table>
      </td>
    </tr>
  </table>
- Notes:
  * Two rows: headings + content
  * Each column individually styled
  * Third column uses unordered list

