40: FOOTER SECTION
──────────────────────────────────────────────

Footer Table
- Syntax:
  <table width="100%" border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="5" bgcolor="#000000">
    <tr>
      <td align="center">
        <font face="Verdana, Geneva, sans-serif" color="#FFFFFF">
          Home | About | Services | Clients | Contact
          <br>
          &copy; 2025 My Business
        </font>
      </td>
    </tr>
  </table>
- Notes:
  * Background color black (#000000)
  * Font color white
  * Navigation labels + copyright
  * Center-aligned content

──────────────────────────────────────────────
Key Notes – Videos 36–40
──────────────────────────────────────────────
- Tables structure: text sections, buttons, forms, three-column content, footer
- Nested tables control width, alignment, spacing
- Alignments: horizontal (left, center, right), vertical (top, middle, bottom)
- Font tags for style (face, size, color) – replace with CSS later
- Forms: POST method, action set to PHP script
- Placeholder links: href="#" until actual links implemented
